replies.msg:
Mignolet's agent Nico Vaesen: &ldquo;It doesn't change the situation (Alisson's arrival). Our goal is to find a solution for Simon to play and Alisson's arrival doesn't change that.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Vaesen: &ldquo;We know that a player of &euro;60-70million won't find himself on the bench. We are looking at the situation and looking for a solution to his playing time. There are options, the next few days will be decisive.&rdquo;

